INSERT INTO `dz_article` VALUES ('343', '34', '深圳美百年文创会所-东方轻盈灰', '项目名称：深圳美百年文创会所-东方轻盈灰\r\n设计公司：Q+设计\r\n项目风格：现代东方\r\n项目面积：1000平米\r\n项目地址：中国·深圳\r\n设计类型：文创会所', '<p style=\"white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 5px; line-height: normal; text-align: left; margin-top: 5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;\">空间散发的文化韵味总能直击内心的柔软，作为商业柔和艺术的载体，文创会所一直在为商业赋予别样的属性，也为当下新的交互方式寻求另一种空间。<br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 5px; text-align: left; margin-top: 5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;\">有别于传统设计的用意在前厅便初露端倪，迎面的大片玻璃营造了空间的光亮通透。而人造光，以几何线条的美感从天花引至地面，光与影交互而生，若隐若浮，操纵着色影深浅。以前厅为引，白色与灰褐垫定了整体空间的两大基调，灰中透着轻盈，质朴中彰显高级。开放性的空间布局，分隔有致。空间与色彩的分离，使得方位之间，既远犹近；可触与未及之处，界限清晰而柔和。墙面与天花装饰极为简约，自然的光感穿梭其间，复制着光阴的印迹。延绵的白色，干净剔透，一束杏黄花，瞬间点缀了一簇嫣然。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 5px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;\">软装摈弃了高饱和度色调，选以灰蓝、淡赭等，即便是暗金色元素，其明度较低，既彰显内敛的奢华，也与空间格调相互契合。中式隔断的艺术手法增添空间雅与境的美感，对古典园林艺术的借用，以现代手法演绎了另一番意趣，对望两端，如跨越于在古典与现代之间，可望，可游，可品。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: normal; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;\">The cultural charm of space is always able to directly hit the inner softness. As a carrier of commercial soft art, Wenchuang Club has always given other attributes to business, and also seeks another space for the new interaction mode.</span></p><p style=\"line-height: normal; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;\">Different from the traditional design, the intention is to be revealed in the front hall. The large glass on the front makes the space bright and transparent. Artificial light, from the ceiling to the ground with the beauty of geometric lines, the interaction between light and shadow, if it is hidden, manipulate the shade of the shadow. In the former hall, the white and gray-brown pads set the two keynotes of the overall space. The gray is light and the simplicity is high. The open space layout is separated. The separation of space and color makes the azimuths both far and near; the touches are inaccessible and the boundaries are clear and soft. The wall and ceiling decoration is extremely simple, and the natural light feels through it, replicating the imprint of time. The white stretches, clean and clear, a bunch of apricot flowers, instantly embellished with a cluster of stunned.</span></p><p style=\"line-height: normal; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;\">The soft decoration rejects the high-saturation color tone, and is selected as gray-blue, light-colored, etc. Even the dark gold element has a low brightness, which not only shows the restrained luxury, but also fits the space style. The artistic method of Chinese partitions adds the beauty of space and the beauty of the environment. The borrowing of classical garden art uses modern techniques to interpret another interest. On both ends of the watch, such as between classical and modern, it is expected to swim. , can be.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></strong></span><br/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190326/1553592468464485.jpg\" title=\"1553592468464485.jpg\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1066\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190326/1553592468969142.jpg\" title=\"1553592468969142.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190326/1553592468354684.jpg\" title=\"1553592468354684.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190326/1553592468570848.jpg\" title=\"1553592468570848.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190326/1553592468207514.jpg\" title=\"1553592468207514.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/u