INSERT INTO `dz_article` VALUES ('369', '34', '港邑翡翠珠宝店', '项目名称：昆明港邑翡翠珠宝店\r\n设计公司：Q+设计\r\n项目面积：100平米\r\n项目风格：现代东方\r\n项目地址：中国·昆明\r\n设计类型：商业空间', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">玉文化我国传承了几千年的文化。</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">它浓集了中华翡翠文化的丰富内涵，是华夏传统文化百花园中的一朵光彩夺目的奇葩，俗话说：</span>“<span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">玉必有意，意必吉祥。</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">”</span></span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">设计师接到本案时，第一时间想到的是如何能够更好的体现</span>“<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">玉的价值</span>”<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">，就如我们标题所说的那样</span>“<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">压箱底的宝贝</span>”<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">一样，当我们看到玉器陈列在柜台时不禁让人想起祖辈总是把</span>“<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">传家宝</span>”<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">收藏在家里的陈旧的宝箱中。设计师平面的设计，采用了中国古代的</span>“<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">八卦</span>”<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">流线设计，目的就是为了让顾客坐在这样的环境里，可以一览无余，将这里所有的玉器展示尽收眼底！设计师利用白色纱蔓垂吊下来做成灯具，表达了设计师对中国一种特有的含蓄、朦胧的美，融进了整个空间，柔和的光照在这些精美的玉器上，使整个空间温文、宁静、含蓄、纯净！</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">设计师通过祖辈收藏</span>“<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">传家宝</span>”<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">的宝箱为元素，在我们祖辈中自己视为最珍贵的东西都会用一个精致的箱子把它好好收藏起来。设计师巧妙的运用这个概念，通过现代的表现手法设计成翡翠店里的展示柜和展示墙，进入店里一把普通的铁壶装饰让我们祖辈的生活历历在目，不仅为陈列在这里的每一件玉器都赋予了最高的艺术气质，也注重了藏品的商业价值！</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">岁月无所谓长短，人生也无所谓长短。为着一个寄托，向着一个目标，过尽岁月，这就是本案设计师的初衷，通过我们的设计，将每一件玉器都视为</span>“<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">压箱底的宝贝</span>”<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">，从而激发客户的购买欲，更让客户觉得自己投入的是一种情怀的寄托，一种文化的传承！</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-size: 12px;\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;\">Jade culture China has inherited thousands of years of culture. It has concentrated the rich connotation of Chinese jade culture, and it is a dazzling and wonderful flower in the Chinese traditional culture garden. As the saying goes: &quot;Jade will be intentional and will be auspicious.&quot;</span></p><p style=\"line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;\">When the designer received the case, the first thing that came to mind was how to better reflect the value of “Jade,” as we said in the title, “The baby at the bottom of the box.” When we saw the jade displayed on the counter. Can&#39;t help but remind people that their ancestors always keep the &quot;heirloom treasure&quot; in the old treasure chest at home. The designer&#39;s flat design adopts the ancient Chinese &quot;gossip&quot; streamline design, the purpose is to let customers sit in such an environment, you can see at a glance, all the jade displays here are all in sight! The designer used the white gauze to hang down to make the lamps, expressing the designer&#39;s unique subtle and sly beauty to China, blending into the space, soft lighting on these beautiful jade, making the whole space gentle, Quiet, subtle, pure!</span></p><p style=\"line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;\">The designer uses the treasure box of the ancestors&#39; collection “Heirloom” as an element. What we consider to be the most precious things in our ancestors will be collected in a delicate box. The designer cleverly uses this concept to design the display cabinet and display wall in the jade shop through modern expression techniques. Entering the ordinary iron pot decoration in the store makes the life of our ancestors vivid, not only for the exhibition here. Each piece of jade gives the highest artistic temperament and also pays attention to the commercial value of the collection!</span></p><p style=\"line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;\">Years don&#39;t matter, and life doesn&#39;t matter. For a sustenance, to a goal, to live through the years, this is the original intention of the designer of this case, through our design, each piece of jade is regarded as the &quot;baby at the bottom of the pressure box&quot;, thus stimulating customers&#39; desire to purchase, let The customer feels that he is investing in a kind of sentiment, a cultural heritage!</span></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553828847754962.jpg\" title=\"1553828847754962.jpg\" alt=\"1.JPG\"/><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553822557897607.jpg\" title=\"1553822557897607.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553822557872856.jpg\" title=\"1553822557872856.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553822557814384.jpg\" title=\"1553822557814384.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553822557999573.jpg\" title=\"1553822557999573.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553822557247983.jpg\" title=\"1553822557247983.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553822557304720.jpg\" title=\"1553822557304720.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553822558172319.jpg\" title=\"1553822558172319.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553822558858366.jpg\" title=\"1553822558858366.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553822558826866.jpg\" title=\"1553822558826866.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p>', 'qjadmin', '1', '0', '/public/uploads/20190329/0304b9f247f9ba11c7f67b70d6c88fc0.JPG', 'a:1:{i:0;s:52:\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553829016699255.jpg\";}', '0', '0', '0', '2019-03-29 09:22:57', '2019-03-29 09:21:02', '', '昆明港邑翡翠珠宝店', '100平米', 'Q+室内设计', '现代东方', '商业空间', '中国·昆明', '', 'Gangyi jade jewelry store', '', '');
INSERT INTO `dz_article` VALUES ('370', '34', '设计师的根据地', '项目名称：设计师的根据地\r\n设计公司：Q+设计\r\n项目面积：300平米\r\n项目风格：现代东方\r\n项目地址：中国·昆明\r\n设计类型：办公空间', '<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">本案是一个开放式的办公空间，从功能性的角度看，设计师通过白色隔断的方式，“景中有景”，将“借景、”框景”手法运用其中，层层渗透，开放的同时，也有效的区分了空间，整个空间在动线功能分区上更加开放、自由、彼此相互连接，让距离感消失，将工作和生活进行融合。整体空间的中心是设计师精心设计的会仪桌，两边是办公桌，同事之间在同一个空间里工作，营造出一个平等的交流空间，同时也保证了有效的沟通与信息传输，为了强化交流，品茶区也是可以愉快的休闲交流，与会议桌的设计相辅相成，团队员工可以根据不同的人，不同的形式，选择不同的方式进行沟通，从而激励团队员工在舒适休闲的环境进行交流与探索。<br/>从美学角度来分析，设计师将中国特有的东方美学特质融入其中，没有采用传统的中式元素来设计，反而大胆的将多种色彩融合到空间中，大量的留白手法，结合传统绘画白描黑色线条的应用，即可以将界、面形成对比，又可以保护边角不受到损坏，巧妙的把“国之精髓”贯穿于空间中，偶尔的“中国红”点缀不但活跃了整个空间，还有利于激发员工的想象力和创造力，同时也体现了本案设计师本身安静，沉稳外表下的热情与张力！地面更是采用了传统的灰色六角砖来铺贴，配以风化久远的实木茶台装饰，更加突出了设计师“文人墨客”的素朴情怀，使整个现代空间显得自然、随性……在这里，能阅读、思考、发呆亦或看看窗外的风景，每一个有关生活真实之美的想法和设计，都是美好的！</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-size: 12px;\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-size: 12px;\">This case is an open office space. From a functional point of view, the designer uses the white partition method, “the scenery in the scene”, and the “borrowing scene” and “frame scene” techniques are applied, and the layers are infiltrated and open at the same time. It also effectively distinguishes the space. The whole space is more open, free and connected to each other in the functional division of the moving line, so that the sense of distance disappears and the work and life are merged. The center of the whole space is the designer&#39;s carefully designed meeting table. On both sides of the desk, colleagues work in the same space, creating an equal communication space, while also ensuring effective communication and information transmission. In order to strengthen communication, the tea area is also a pleasant leisure exchange. The design of the conference table complements each other. Team employees can communicate in different ways according to different people and different forms, thus motivating team members to communicate and explore in a comfortable and leisure environment.</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-size: 12px;\">From the aesthetic point of view, the designer incorporates the unique oriental aesthetics of China into it. Instead of using traditional Chinese elements to design, it boldly blends multiple colors into the space, a large number of white techniques, combined with traditional painting and black painting. The application of lines can contrast the boundaries and faces, and protect the corners from damage. Cleverly put the essence of the country into the space. The occasional &quot;China Red&quot; embellishment not only activates the whole space, but also facilitates Inspire the imagination and creativity of the staff, but also reflects the enthusiasm and tension of the designer&#39;s own quiet, calm appearance! The ground is made of traditional gray hexagonal bricks, decorated with a long-lasting solid wood tea table decoration, which highlights the simple feelings of the designer “literary literati”, making the whole modern space look natural and casual...here You can read, think, daze or look at the scenery outside the window. Every idea and design about the true beauty of life is wonderful!</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><br/></span><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://qq.qiqifeng.top/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553823229474573.jpg\" title=\"1553823229474573.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553823228725499.jpg\" title=\"1553823228725499.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553823228577662.jpg\" title=\"1553823228577662.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553823228451151.jpg\" title=\"1553823228451151.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553823229329819.jpg\" title=\"1553823229329819.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553823229621711.jpg\" title=\"1553823229621711.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553823229274462.jpg\" title=\"1553823229274462.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553823229728884.jpg\" title=\"1553823229728884.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://qq.qiqifeng.top/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553823228695165.jpg\" title=\"1553823228695165.jpg\"/><img src=\"http://qq.qiqifeng.top/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553823228547925.jpg\" title=\"1553823228547925.jpg\"/></p>', 'qjadmin', '1', '0', '/public/uploads/20190329/db8f0d9b4fbc05e74da646bffdaf4b96.jpg', 'a:1:{i:0;s:52:\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553829117948362.jpg\";}', '0', '0', '0', '2019-03-29 09:34:04', '2019-03-29 09:22:58', '', '设计师的根据地', '300平米', 'Q+室内设计', '现代东方', '办公空间', '中国·昆明', '', 'The Base of Designers', '', '');
INSERT INTO `dz_article` VALUES ('371', '34', '维多利亚高级美发会所', '项目名称：维多利亚高级美发会所\r\n设计公司：Q+设计\r\n项目面积：1000平米\r\n项目风格：现代东方\r\n项目地址：中国·昆明\r\n设计类型：商业空间', '<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-size: 12px;\">本案的设计灵感来源于中国水墨画的意境美，从中国水墨画中找出表现手法，找到神的表现，简洁的线与留白色彩关系的整体对比，将对现实与自然的提炼，通过结构形式的简化，当代的手法，实现了作品的内在平衡。刚与柔，虚与实的对比，营造出空灵、清丽、明快，抒情的意境。线在空间中穿插，又富有变化及律动，情韵自然。以单纯、留白有力的块面，飞舞的线条，将复杂的事物归纳、锤炼成单纯、素净的造型，形成一种具有中国文化精神和现代形式美感的风格。和谐而清新的色调，宁静而恬淡的境界，使本案的设计产生一种有抒情诗般的感染力。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-size: 12px;\">The design of this case is inspired by the artistic conception of Chinese ink painting. From the Chinese ink painting to find the expression technique, to find the performance of God, the overall contrast between the simple line and the white color, the refinement of reality and nature, through the structural form Simplified, contemporary methods, the internal balance of the work. The contrast between softness and emptiness and reality creates an ethereal, clear, bright, and lyrical mood. The lines are interspersed in space, and they are full of changes and rhythms. With simple, white and powerful blocks and flying lines, the complex things are summarized and tempered into simple and plain shapes, forming a style with Chinese cultural spirit and modern form aesthetics. The harmonious and fresh color, quiet and bleak realm, makes the design of this case have a lyrical appeal.<img src=\"http://qq.qiqifeng.top/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553823329768107.jpg\" title=\"1553823329768107.jpg\"/></span></p><p><img src=\"http://qq.qiqifeng.top/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553823328317111.jpg\" title=\"1553823328317111.jpg\"/><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553823328279686.jpg\" title=\"1553823328279686.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553823329637623.jpg\" title=\"1553823329637623.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553823329122278.jpg\" title=\"1553823329122278.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553823329390536.jpg\" title=\"1553823329390536.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553823329721846.jpg\" title=\"1553823329721846.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553823329910013.jpg\" title=\"1553823329910013.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553823329777783.jpg\" title=\"1553823329777783.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553823329303182.jpg\" title=\"1553823329303182.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553823330337349.jpg\" title=\"1553823330337349.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p>', 'qjadmin', '1', '0', '/public/uploads/20190329/0463b4fb3b70d9f4e433caf0e87f57cc.jpg', 'a:1:{i:0;s:52:\"/public/uploads/images/20190329/1553827059335523.jpg\";}', '0', '0', '0', '2019-03-29 09:35:52', '2019-03-29 09:34:05', '', '维多利亚高级美发会所', '1000平米', 'Q+室内设计', '现代东方', '商业空间', '中国·昆明', '', 'Victoria Advanced Hair Salon', '', '');
